Business Brief -- First of America Bank Corp.:
   Firm Expects to Post Net
   Of Up to 87 Cents a Share
First of America "normally is not pleased with a modest
increase in earnings per share," Mr. Smith said. "But as far
as the rest of the {banking} industry is concerned, it's a
good showing."
   Mr. Smith added that the company foresees "very strong
earnings increases this year" before some one-time charges
related to its acquisition of Security Bancorp Inc. in
Michigan.